#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thag1.8:4.1"
msgid "1.8. Vīrattheragāthā"
msgstr "1.8. Vīra"

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="vns" id="vns8"></a><a class="vnp" id="vnp8"></a>
msgctxt "thag1.8:5.1"
msgid "“Yo duddamiyo damena danto,"
msgstr "Once hard to tame, now tamed himself;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.8:5.2"
msgid "Vīro santusito vitiṇṇakaṅkho;"
msgstr "a hero, content, with doubt overcome;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.8:5.3"
msgid "Vijitāvī apetalomahaṃso,"
msgstr "victorious, with goosebumps vanished,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.8:5.4"
msgid "Vīro so parinibbuto ṭhitatto”ti."
msgstr "Vīra is steadfast, and has become extinguished."

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "thag1.8:6.1"
msgid "Itthaṃ sudaṃ āyasmā vīro thero gāthaṃ abhāsitthāti."
msgstr "It was thus that this verse was recited by the senior venerable Vīra."
